-- Scott Leads Snedeker by One Shot in Third Round of British Open
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-07-21T15:36:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-21/scott-leads-snedeker-by-one-shot-in-third-round-of-british-open.html
Australia’s  Adam Scott  holds a one-
shot lead over American Brandt Snedeker in the third round of
golf’s British Open.  Scott is 9 under par after starting his round with six
straight pars. Snedeker made his first two bogeys of the
tournament at the fifth and sixth holes to drop to 8 under.  Tiger Woods and Ernie Els are tied for third place at 5
under. Woods is 1 over par after six holes and Els is two under
through nine.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  